{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">INFO</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game requires <strong>two players</strong> and a <strong>headset</strong> for seamless communication.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119740/extras/uh1Descrp.png?t=1734969484\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">About</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your crew consists of the best two thieves money can buy\u2014no questions asked. That\u2019s how it\u2019s always been, until a mysterious client hires you to steal an unknown item. The target? Classified. The pay? Too good to pass up. Decide who will handle intel and who will infiltrate the facility in this high-stakes asymmetric co-op puzzle game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2119740/extras/gameplay.gif?t=1734969484\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Unique Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Asymmetric Co-op.</strong> Work in separate places, using tools and solving puzzles to help each other.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Engaging Heist Story.</strong> Discover a story with twists, multiple endings, and choices that matter.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Creative Puzzles.</strong> Solve puzzles with new ideas that make teamwork essential.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>In-Game Voice Chat.</strong> Use an old-school walkie-talkie to stay in touch with your partner.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Striking Level Design.</strong> Explore bold environments built to inspire and challenge you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enjoy the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">~ No More Sleep</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Spinning heads","p